Changes:
  Add support for the new perk deck;
  Fix code to be compatible with update 49;
  Fix money calculations to be more accurate;
  Change cost depending on player level. At level 0, full price. At level 100 or above (infamous), free.
    - Reasoning: Payday 2's skill profiles unlock based on the player's level. The last unlock is at level 100 and is kept after going infamous.

New known bug:
  The skills don't save if the user quits the game after changing his build without entering another menu.
